A 42-year-old man Terhemen Iorbee has hung himself on a tree. The deceased was an indigene of Mbakuha Council ward of Ushongo Local Government in Benue State. He was married with four children.   New Police dress code illegal – Adegboruwa     Lagos to probe petrol souvenir at party     How 22-year-old lady got ‘missing’ BRT bus   Iorbee’s body was found dangling on the tree on Saturday. It was gathered the deceased, who was a native doctor, started behaving strangely recently. The deceased, though married to three wives, had been living alone. He was said to have gone missing on Friday only for his body to be found hanging on a tree.